 1- rby ḥyạty tḥlw bḥbk .. lys swạk rby ḥbyb
 tmlk qlby ạ̉sẖdw yqynaⁿạ .. mʿk jrạḥy swf tṭyb
 ạlqrạr- hạ ʿrsẖ qlby wmlʾ ḥby .. wkl ʿmry wṭạʿty
 lys klạmaⁿạ wlạ ạ̹nfʿạlaⁿạ .. bạlṣdq ậty bjmlty
 2- rwḥk rby qwẗ ḥby .. yrtẖy lḍʿfy ysẖfʿ fy
 ymlk dẖạty kl ḥyạty .. ạ̉sẖhd ʿnk ḥlwuⁿ ly
 3- bhjẗ ʿmry ạ̉ḥyạ lsẖkẖṣk .. ạ̉ḥyạ lrby ạ̉gẖly̱ rfyq
 ḥyn ạ̉sr ybqy̱ srwry .. bslạm rby wqt ạlḍyq
 4- rby ạ̹lyk ạ̉dnw bqlby .. hdẖy ḥyạty mạdẖạ tryd
 wʿdk yʿṭy nfsy yqynaⁿạ .. ạ̉tẖmr fyk bl wạ̉zyd</lyrics>
